  "detailed_description": "Two game modes: stage defender and stage control<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897400/extras/8a03d9175174733921d37e8ecdf4cdaa.avif?t=1671546015\" width=600 height=204 /></span><br><br>Control your stage lights & effects with drumsticks: LEDs, pyrotechnics, smoke, lasers, holograms and a giant screen camera.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897400/extras/92467651fad60a01f69aace51ddaf8a5.poster.avif?t=1671546015\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897400/extras/92467651fad60a01f69aace51ddaf8a5.webm?t=1671546015\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897400/extras/92467651fad60a01f69aace51ddaf8a5.mp4?t=1671546015\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>36 characters to customize your stage: singers, dancers, musicians.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897400/extras/57d81b6b7d229e0400f5437232750f1a.avif?t=1671546015\" width=600 height=204 /></span><br><br>Enjoy your mp3 music on your hard drive : Rock, Pop, Classical, Reggae, Rap, Metal...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897400/extras/282dcf5fd194ae1bfbbcccb1a3933335.avif?t=1671546015\" width=600 height=204 /></span><br><br>Two game modes: stage defender and stage control<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897400/extras/253d3d60db259aff105de32c40dc7000.avif?t=1671546015\" width=600 height=204 /></span><br><br>Oculus Quest 2 + link 